# === Reserved tables (documented to prevent future-conflict) ===
# [regex]            ÔÇö globbing is out of scope for v1.0
# [icon_colors]      ÔÇö per-icon color overrides; v1.1 candidate
# [type_overrides]   ÔÇö file-type glyphs (folder, link, ...);
